<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6552196>
    dc:description "FIGURE. 7. Telebasis noveloi: a, male in lateral view (Tadó, Chocó); Unión Panamericana, Chocó: b, pair in tandem; c, male dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6552196/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6552190>
    dc:description "FIGURE. 5. Telebasis noveloi male: head dorsal view: a, predominantly blue specimen (Tadó, Chocó); b, greenish blue specimen (Unión Panamericana, Chocó); Tadó, Chocó: genital ligula: c, ecto-lateral view; d, lateral view; caudal appendages: e, lateral view; f, dorso-lateral view; g, dorsal view; h, dorso-lateral view (covered with white pruinescence). b. t.: blunt tip; i. f.: inner fold; t.: ventral tooth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6552190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6552194>
    dc:description "FIGURE. 6. Telebasis noveloi female: a, head dorsal view (Tadó, Chocó); b, S8–10 lateral view (Unión Panamericana, Chocó); Tadó, Chocó: prothorax and anterior region of pterothorax: c, dorsal view; d, lateral view. ml. r.: medio-lateral ridge; pit.: pits behind mesepisternal plates." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6552194/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6552188>
    dc:description "FIGURE. 4. Distribution map of Telebasis blasi and T. noveloi in the Western Andes foothills and biogeographic Chocó lowlands." ;
